Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather doesn't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Miss, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go to John's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh-ah-ah-ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it go to John!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,UNKNOWN PLACES. SEARCH FOR LASSIE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what you have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This will discredit our family!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You only have to recognize what you have done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that dog knows the location\Nof the village of Greenor Bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it's in Scotland,\Nwhich is 400 miles away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've just left the dog mess around!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mess around? What a terrible analogy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter if this is the promise\Nthat John made to you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you should've thought about Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that is promise that men do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you thought about what would happen\Nif the coal didn't come out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So what will you do for John and Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be separated because of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather, in the end\Nyou wanted to own Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Priscilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie may face many people\Nwho want to own it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand very well how\Nyour heart feels about that dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't guarantee that some\Nhonorable people will pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well well... It's better to hope\Nthat Lassie will have good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Look, Willy!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eh, it looks like a good dog!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a wonderful dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why it hangs around\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be great to stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... just come...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to fear and stay still
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Willie!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be a runaway from the Duke's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If we catch that dog we'll get a great bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, he must be hiding here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ay! Don't throw the stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to wound it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But we won't catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? A message? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop joking and tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Priscilla Rodoring?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, from Scotland! It's from Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It fled from their palace in Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It left the palace...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He went directly south...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone saw Lassie walking south!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To the South...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It says the South!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If it will go south, it will\Nreach Yorkshire, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie returns home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We must find coal in any way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie goes home, so I won't\Nlet it go anywhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do, teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only a fan of Loch Ness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish the monster would appear again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is suitable\Nfor drawing pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit interesting...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking at the lake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That dog looks so precious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to want to go to\Nthe far side of the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You are like the poets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it wants to cross the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow the dog did it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why it went across this lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure there's something precious about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I were alone I could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then Jimmy ate everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So funny!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Jimmy eat at last?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is true!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hesitate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to eat and you'll be comfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And now take it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John, I have published\Nthis ad in the newspaper.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyone who sees this beautiful Collie dog â€‹\Nmay contact me for a reward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, is it similar to what was\Npublished in the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I noticed that Lassie was\Nheading south directly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it is heading straight to London.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie... continues to travel to your city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The picture I sent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Loch Ness in Scotland,\Nit was standing in that exact spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's get away from this dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya-ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}xxx{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you, you dirty dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be harmful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What it did this suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He suddenly became calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, get it in the car quickly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He fled into the court!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go to the defendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? It come here to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize, I'll catch it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, what a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father, in there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, the sheep will be attacked again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's another one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you sure?\N- I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be your imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a voice behind the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Something seems to be suffering terribly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear any sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and see! It's a big dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... This wound is made by gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shot this dog with a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Last week I got Tommy's mail\Nfrom the neighboring town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In that place the sheep were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from the owners of the barn\Ncomplaining about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If this dog attacked the sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not so, Dan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This dog can't attack the sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how you feel again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you make a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But you also agree with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we move to this house because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Well maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haven't you wake up yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Breakfast is ready!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, I'm coming!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie came from upstairs\Nto the kitchen ahead of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Say something like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie is lazy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you warm milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feed it with milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing wrong with\Nbreakfast sometimes with milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My God! My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is rare for an English man\Nto drink tea instead of milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm the only one complaining here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can stand now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Four days have already passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, close the door immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Purcell will come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Purcell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You are barely able to walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Danny went to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When we left, no one else stayed at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You are also satisfied with Purcell's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly became like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He will be fine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Purcell went far beyond the war.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is impossible to return again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm... This is true!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This picture was taken a week ago in court.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that, I don't know where Lassie is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm sure it is in good health!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It will continue his journey\Nuntil it reaches you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Purcell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't open the door, Dan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Purcell, you can't go out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wound has not healed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Purcell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make us sad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have more health,\Nyou will be very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I enter please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear, it's okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he always does that at three o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is he aiming for at three o'clock?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow we don't see it anymore, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen John!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It will certainly come soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie will definitely sit\Nnext time there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Purcell? Isn't it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Purcell... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that oatmeal\Nthis morning is a bit different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not be happy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you notice only at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You care about it a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Purcell's eyes are nice,\Nbut his eyes are still very sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like Danny's return when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why don't we let Purcell go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Danny was little,\Nhe loved walking in the forest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But Purcell has hurt his leg not long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know very well that\Nits injury has become much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes out of here\Nit won't come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems to be traveling to a certain place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This house is just a passing place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we can do it with our hands gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We may hurt it more without knowing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We also lived a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It might come back to us, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Before Purcell came
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I will continue to live happily with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Purcell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you really have a name, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go where you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Also be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true, this is the most important thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happy now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That 's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was back in the mine after\Nwe discovered something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't know yet where Lassie is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do your best, Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will definitely find you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\NWELCOME BACK, LASSIE{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.17,0:22:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
